OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,FJustice Minister Naomi Long said she
OL,7,Fhas not ruled out an appeal against a
OL,8,FHigh Court ruling on a challenge to
OL,9,Fsexual offence anonymity laws.
OL,11,FThe Sexual Offences and Trafficking
OL,12,FVictims Act came into force in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland last year.
OL,15,FIt excludes the public from Crown
OL,16,FCourt rape cases and also provides
OL,17,Fanonymity for suspects in sexual
OL,18,Foffence cases up to the point of
OL,19,Fcharge.
