OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,FThose not subsequently charged will
OL,7,Fhave anonymity for their lifetime and
OL,8,Ffor 25 years after their death.
OL,10,FMedia organisations launched a legal
OL,11,Fchallenge against sections 12 to 16 of
OL,12,Fthe Act, in concern at the impact on
OL,13,Fthe reporting of sexual offence
OL,14,Fallegations.
OL,16,FAn example given was that the
OL,17,Flegislation would have prevented media
OL,18,Ffrom being able to report the
OL,19,Fallegations against the disgraced
OL,20,Fentertainer Jimmy Savile.
