OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,FLast week, Mr Justice Humphreys said
OL,7,Fit was beyond Stormont's legislative
OL,8,Fcompetence to introduce the Act which
OL,9,Fhas the.
OL,11,FHe found it was not compatible with
OL,12,Fhuman rights law on press freedom and
OL,13,Ftherefore unlawful.
OL,15,FStormont Opposition leader Matthew
OL,16,FO'Toole put an urgent oral question to
OL,17,FMs Long in the Assembly on Monday
OL,18,Fabout what actions she plans to take
OL,19,Ffollowing the ruling.
