OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,FResponding, Ms Long said it was a
OL,7,Fcomplex judgment and she wants to take
OL,8,Ftime to study the detail with her
OL,9,Fdepartment's legal team.
OL,11,F"The judgment found in favour of the
OL,12,Fapplicants in respect of the challenge
OL,13,Fthat the provision was incompatible
OL,14,Fwith article 10 of the European
OL,15,FConvention on Human Rights, which is
OL,16,Fthe right to freedom of expression,
OL,17,Fand declared it unlawful," she told
OL,18,FMLAs.
