OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,F"I will now wish to study the detail
OL,7,Fof the judgment in conjunction with my
OL,8,Fdepartment's legal team before making
OL,9,Fany decisions on a way forward."
OL,11,FShe was pressed further by Mr O'Toole,
OL,12,Fwho said it was "terrible law", and
OL,13,Fany attempt to appeal against the
OL,14,Fjudgment would be "doubling down on
OL,15,Fbad law and be a waste of public
OL,16,Fmoney".
