OL,3,CNI sex anonymity law appeal 'always an
OL,4,Coption,' says Long
OL,6,FMs Long responded: "As I have already
OL,7,Fsaid, this is a complex and detailed
OL,8,Flegal judgment, and it does not just
OL,9,Fhave implications for this particular
OL,10,Fpiece of legislation, but potentially
OL,11,Falso for this House.
OL,13,F"Appeal is therefore always an option.
OL,15,F"However, I will want to carefully
OL,16,Fconsider all my available options and
OL,17,Fin conjunction with the department's
OL,18,Flegal team before arriving at a
OL,19,Fdecision to the best way forward.
